lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>al</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>i Text and ¡¥nissaya¡¦ (word for word
translation) of the Abhidhammatha Sa</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>gaha,
and the Paccaya Niddesa of the Pa</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
Foreign1'>tt</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>h</span><span
