<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>When it is said in the P</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>al</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>i Texts that only when there has been
adhikara in previous Buddha S</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span
