style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>s
can relative jh</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>na, the Paths and the Fruits
be obtained in the following Buddha S</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>san</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>s, the word ¡¥adhik</span><span
