style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ra. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Of
the two kinds of seeds, those people who encounter a Buddha S</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>san</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>,
but who fail to secure the seeds of vijj</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>,
suffer great loss indeed. This is so because the seeds of vijj</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> which are related to r</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>u</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>pa and n</span><span lang=EN-US
