Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>san</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> or within the S</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>san</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> of the next Buddha, 3) they can derive
immense benefit from their existence as human beings during the Buddha S</span><span
