style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US>-Dhamma of the Present
Day: A Word of Advice And Warning</span></span></span></h4>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>If the Tipi</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>t</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>aka
which are the discourses of the Buddha delivered during forty-five vassas
