<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The definition of sammappadh</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>n</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
is: <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Bhusa</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1;mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>m</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> dhahati vahatiti padhana</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1;mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>m</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>,<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre
style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Sammadeva padhana</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1;mso-bidi-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>m</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span><span lang=EN-US
