<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>(Let only my skin, and sinews,
and bones remain, and let my flesh and blood in the body dry up, I shall not
permit the course of my effort to stop until I win that which may be won by
human ability, human effort and human exertion.) <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>These characteristics may be summed up as
follows: <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul type=disc>
 <ol start=1 type=1>
  <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
      auto;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;tab-stops:list 72.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
      style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>let the skin, remain <o:p></o:p></span></li>
  <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
      auto;mso-list:l2 level2 lfo6;tab-stops:list 72.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
      style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>let the sinews remain <o:p></o:p></span></li>
