lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>mavacara knowledge and wisdom,
and abhinna,[79] such as dibba-cakkhu (the celestial eye) and dibba-sota (the
celestial ear). <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>When it is said that effort must be made
to transform this pa</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>bba</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> into niyama, it must be
