style='font-family:Foreign1'>tt</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>hi.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>If they desire to free themselves from the
insane and wild mind such as is possessed by the mad man, the incapable
