style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga,
(the alms-food-eater¡¦s ascetic practice), nesajjika</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga
(the sitter¡¦s ascetic practice), rukkhamulika</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga
(the tree-root-dweller¡¦s ascetic practice), abbhokasika</span><span lang=EN-US
