lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>riya. From the moment k</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>yagata-sati is set up, the viriya that
