lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>ban</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>a.[98] <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>This shows how the five indriya occur
