<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>In this world, the strength of builders
lie in good tools, such as awls, chisels, axes, knives, saws, etc. Only when he
equips himself with such strength can he undertake to build monasteries,
houses, etc. In the work of carpenters, blacksmiths, goldsmiths, artists,
wood-carvers, etc., also, they have each their respective strength. Their
strength consists of good tools and implements. Only with such can they
accomplish their work. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

