lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga, is sati-sambojjha</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The pa</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>bba</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'>-cetasika called vimamsiddhipada, pa</span><span lang=EN-US
