style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>-</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>ban</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'>a are called dhammavicaya-sambojjha</span><span lang=EN-US
