Just as cotton seeds are milled, carded, etc., so as to produce cotton wool,
the process of repeatedly viewing the five khandha with the functions of
vipassan</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>-</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>ban</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Times New Roman"'>a is called dhammavicaya. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The v</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>i</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>riya-cetasika
