piti-sambojjha</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>v</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The process of becoming calm and tranquil
in both body and mind when the mental distractions, reflections, aides thoughts
abate, is called passaddhi-sambojjha</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
Foreign1'>v</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ga. It
is the cetasika of k</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ya-passaddhi and
citta-passaddhi. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>The sam</span><span lang=EN-US
