style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
there are two kinds of heritages, namely, good and bad. There are also two
kinds of heirs, namely, good and bad. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>I shall here show the essentials in the
Dhamma Dayada Sutta,[154] Mula Pannasa, Majjhiina Nik</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:Foreign1'>a</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>ya.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dhamma dayada me bhikkhave bhavattha,<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre
style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>ma amisadayada.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Atthi me tumhesu anukampa.<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre
