(dwelling place constructed in a lonely place at the foot of a tree), and putimutta
medicine (strong smelling urine of cattle used as medicine). These fourtre
called Buddhadayajja. They are the four great heritages which the Buddha
approved. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>If that is the case, it needs to be
