<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Atireka lobho viharo addhayogo, etc,.<br>
(Surplus monastery, dwelling place, etc.) <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
