<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>It is to reveal this path that the
Buddha, in several places of the Suttanta and Abhidhamma Pi</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Foreign1'>t</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>akas said: <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Tinnam samyojanam parikkhaya sotapanno hoti,<o:p></o:p></span></pre><pre
style='margin-left:36.0pt'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>avinipata dhammo niyato sambodhiparayano. [162]<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin-left:36.0pt;tab-stops:24.0pt'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>(Because the three samyojana cease, the
